ideas.Step_by_Step_Experiment_Plan:
1) Extract and construct time-aware semantic hierarchies from social media and EHR-based knowledge graphs, incorporating semantic role labels and sentiment aspects;
2) Compute semantic drift metrics over temporal slices to formulate dynamic temporal weighting functions;
3) Implement dynamic hierarchical temporal contrastive learning with weighted loss and time-conditioned pair sampling;
4) Evaluate embeddings on downstream tasks involving lexical semantic change detection, mental health signal prediction, and aspect-based sentiment analysis with temporal robustness;
5) Perform embedding space mechanistic analyses linking embedding trajectories to temporal semantic evolution, validating interpretability claims;
6) Conduct ablation studies comparing static vs. dynamic weighting and hierarchical vs. heterogeneous graph integration.
